          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ending Secrecy About Workplace Sexual Harassment Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs every employer required to submit to the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission an Employer Information Report EEO-1 to include in such report the number of settlements reached in the resolution of claims pertaining to sex discrimination.</p>]]></text>
